articles.author: Tim Zadorozhnyy
articles.title: Russian missile that hit government headquarters contained over 30 foreign-made parts, Ukraine says - The Kyiv Independent
articles.description: "Compared to missiles from previous years, there are fewer components from Europe and the U.S., and more from Russia and Belarus," presidential sanctions commissioner Vladyslav Vlasiuk said.
